  "texts": [
    "To do this, we simply sort the embeddings of all candidate images or reports by their cosine similarity to the embedding of a query image or report.",
    "The embedding space was normalized to unit vectors before calculation of cosine similarity to be insensitive to projection magnitude.",
    "If the model and dataset were theoretically perfect, we would expect the image or report that is officially paired with the query image or report to be ranked first in the list.",
    "We report the mean rank number as a metric of accuracy.",
    "This allows us to characterize EchoCLIP-R's retrieval abilities in two settings: image-to-report and report-to-image."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}